[2026-04-18T16:40:28.387Z] [INFO]         "content": "{\"body\":\"## 🤖 Solution Draft Log\\nThis log file contains the complete execution trace of the AI solution draft process.\\n\\n### 💰 **Cost estimation:**\\n- Model: gpt-5.4\\n- Provider: OpenAI\\n- Public pricing estimate: unknown\\n- Token usage: 299,329 input, 41,112 output, 26,229,760 cache read\\n\\n### 📊 **Context and tokens usage:**\\n\\nTotal: (299.3K + 26.2M cached) input tokens, 41.1K output tokens\\n\\n### 🤖 **Models used:**\\n- Tool: OpenAI Codex\\n- Requested: `gpt-5.4`\\n- **Model: GPT-5.4** (`gpt-5.4`)\\n\\n### 📎 **Log file uploaded as Repository** (32650KB)\\n- [View complete solution draft log](https://github.com/konard/log-tmp-solution-draft-log-pr-1776526635930.txt/raw/main/tmp-solution-draft-log-pr-1776526635930.txt)\\n\\n---\\n*Now working session is ended, feel free to review and add any feedback on the solution draft.*\",\"created_at\":\"2026-04-18T15:37:24Z\",\"id\":4274015110,\"user\":\"konard\"}\n{\"body\":\"## 🔄 Auto-restart triggered (iteration 1)\\n\\n**Reason:** Merge conflicts detected\\n\\nStarting new session to address the issues.\\n\\n---\\n*Auto-restart-until-mergeable mode is active. Will continue until PR becomes mergeable.*\",\"created_at\":\"2026-04-18T15:39:29Z\",\"id\":4274018477,\"user\":\"konard\"}\n{\"body\":\"## 🔄 Auto-restart-until-mergeable Log (iteration 1)\\nThis log file contains the complete execution trace of the AI solution draft process.\\n\\n### 💰 **Cost estimation:**\\n- Model: gpt-5.4\\n- Provider: OpenAI\\n- Public pricing estimate: unknown\\n- Token usage: 130,478 input, 17,041 output, 6,018,560 cache read\\n\\n### 🤖 **Models used:**\\n- Tool: OpenAI Codex\\n- Requested: `gpt-5.4`\\n- **Model: GPT-5.4** (`gpt-5.4`)\\n\\n### 📎 **Log file uploaded as Repository** (51312KB)\\n- [View complete solution draft log](https://github.com/konard/log-tmp-solution-draft-log-pr-1776527587017.txt/raw/main/tmp-solution-draft-log-pr-1776527587017.txt)\\n\\n---\\n*Now working session is ended, feel free to review and add any feedback on the solution draft.*\",\"created_at\":\"2026-04-18T15:53:13Z\",\"id\":4274042713,\"user\":\"konard\"}\n{\"body\":\"## ✅ Ready to merge\\n\\nThis pull request is now ready to be merged:\\n- All CI checks have passed\\n- No merge conflicts\\n- No pending changes\\n\\n---\\n*Monitored by hive-mind with --auto-restart-until-mergeable flag*\",\"created_at\":\"2026-04-18T15:55:33Z\",\"id\":4274046401,\"user\":\"konard\"}\n{\"body\":\"We should also disable any atribution for Claude Code:\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nhttps://code.claude.com/docs/en/settings#attribution-settings\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\n{\\r\\n  \\\"attribution\\\": {\\r\\n    \\\"commit\\\": \\\"\\\",\\r\\n    \\\"pr\\\": \\\"\\\"\\r\\n  }\\r\\n}\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nAnd also\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nincludeCoAuthoredBy\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nShould be set explicitly to false.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nprefersReducedMotion\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nShould be set to true, as we use Claude Code in docker or autonomous mode.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nshowThinkingSummaries\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nShould be set to false by default. To reduce load on the system. \\r\\n\\r\\n`spinnerTipsEnabled` to false\\r\\n\\r\\n`viewMode` to `verbose`.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nenv\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nsetting should be set to all the same default variables.\\r\\n\\r\\n```\\r\\nCLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_FAST_MODE\\r\\n```\\r\\n\\r\\nShould be disabled, meaning = 1.\\r\\n\\r\\nDouble check `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_FEEDBACK_SURVEY ` is disabled.\\r\\n\\r\\nCLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_MOUSE also should be set to 1.\\r\\n\\r\\nCLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_AWAY_SUMMARY should be disabled.\\r\\n\\r\\nCLAUDE_CODE_MAX_TOOL_USE_CONCURRENCY should be set to 4.\\r\\n\\r\\nCLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_GIT_INSTRUCTIONS should be enabled back.\\r\\n\\r\\nhttps://code.claude.com/docs/en/env-vars - we should double check what other ENVs we should consider to set for our automated environment. Please report me for options, and I will select what el